某说，冲突的原因是他反对盗版和芯片外包，「因为使用盗版 EDA 工具设计出来的芯片可能有 BUG，我主张公司要有自己的芯片设计研发团队，但有些东西他们不接受。」孙某称他做芯片研发已经有 20 年的工作经历，当初来这家公司工作是被朋友邀请过来的。「被女高管违法开除」员工：并非能力不足，被逼签道歉函才给赔偿 - 上游新闻 汇聚向上的力量"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/638700452"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsLmM9+HF+7VhEAMaCTEwNDIxMTcyNyD01/KsBjAAODBAHnIJNjM4NzAwNDUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1704794786.742122", "card_id": "Q_620407074", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 305}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么有人身处打压式家庭里还能自信起来?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "正常情况下在这种家庭成长的男生普遍自卑，但为什么有的人会「奇特」的成为另外一种自信的「奇葩」存在？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-91d7822bf9a9a93d0b636dc02f8984d1_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620407074"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsLmM9+HF+7VhEAMaCTEwMDE0Nzk2NCCFs9KnBjAAOMMIQB9yCTYyMDQwNzA3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1704794786.743021", "card_id": "Q_638319297", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哈兰德，姆巴佩，贝林厄姆如果三人同队，该怎么组队，才能更好的发挥他们三人的能力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "其实是突然想到了当初的国米，阿德和马丁内斯，一高一快。 简单一点，换成现在，把三个人都放在皇马，该怎么组？ 三个人都放在曼城，又该怎么组？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5091d65453b187ea4438cc5bf04b3f3c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/638319297"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsLmM9+HF+7VhEAMa